Icyorezo cya Coronavirus (COVID-19) muri EU/Afurika y'Ubumwe bw'u Burayi n'Ubwongereza, kuva ku itariki ya 1 Mutarama kugeza ku ya 15 Werurwe 2020
Ibikorwa rusange by'icyorezo cya Coronavirus (COVID-19) bigaragaza impinduka nk'izo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/Akarere k'ubukungu bwa Buraya n'u Bwongereza byemeje ko, mu gihe mu byiciro bitandukanye bivanye n'igihugu, icyorezo cya COVID-19 ku isi hose kigenda cyakwirakwira mu bihugu byose.
Mu rwego rwo gukurikirana abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho byihutirwa, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku byihutirwa, bikwiye kongera ubushake bwo kubikurikirana.
Ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2020, hari itsinda ry'abantu bataramenyekana bafite uburwayi bw'ibicurane mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Tariki ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara cyatangaje impamvu zitera coronavirus nshya ubu yitwa indwara ikomeye yo mu mwuka y'ibimenyetso bya coronavirus 2 ((SARS-CoV-2).
Kugeza ubu, indwara y'indwara ya SARS-CoV-2 yitwa Coronavirus (COVID-19).
Hari ibimenyetso bigaragaza ko hafi 80% by'abantu barwaye COVID-19 baba bafite uburwayi buciriritse, nko guturika mu buryo bwo guhumeka cyangwa kubura ubumuga, kandi akenshi bakira.
Hafi 14% by'abanduye COVID-19 baterwa n'uburwayi bukabije bukeneye ubuvuzi, naho 6% bisigaye bivurwa n'uburwayi bukabije bukeneye kwitabwaho byihuse.
Urupfu rw'abarwayi ba COVID-19 ruba ku kigero cya 4%.
Muri iki cyigisho, tugereranya impinduka mu byiciro byose bya COVID-19 mu bihugu bya EU/EEA na UK, ugereranyije n'akarere ka Hubei. Ubushinwa.
