Twagaragaje umubare w'abanduye muri buri gihugu ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe 2020 saa munani za mu gitondo ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama - 15 Werurwe 2020.
Ihindagurika rya COVID-19 mu bihugu by'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/EEA no mu Bwongereza
Ihinduka ry'iminsi 14 ku munsi ku mubare w'abanduye COVID-19 mu bihugu by'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/EEA no mu Bwongereza, mu by'ukuri rivugwa mu karere ka Hubei (Ubushinwa) (Ifoto 1).
Muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 watangiye kwiyongera ahagana ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, ariko ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare 2020 (Icyiciro cy'ubufasha).
Ibi byatewe n'ubwandu bw'abanduye mu Butaliyani, ariko mu bindi bihugu byose by'umuryango w'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/EEA no mu Bwongereza, umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 uragenda wiyongera.
Igishushanyo cya 2 kigaragaza umubare w'abanduye COVID-19, mu bihugu by'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/ubumwe bwa EEA no mu Bwongereza ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani kuva tariki 31 Mutarama kugeza tariki 15 Werurwe 2020.
Igaragaza ko ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe saa munani z'ijoro, ibindi bihugu 15 byo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/EEA n'u Bwongereza byatangaje umubare w'abanduye ushobora kugereranywa n'uw'u Butaliyani mu byumweru bibiri cyangwa birenga.
Ibyavuye muri iki gikorwa bigaragaza ko umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 wiyongera cyane muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Ihinduka ry'ibyabaye muri rusange bya COVID-19 ritanga igitekerezo cy'uko iki cyorezo cyugarije isi yose cyakwirakwira ku muvuduko ugereranywa n'uw'ibihugu byose.
Ibi bibaho mu gihe ibihugu bitandukanye bifite ibipimo bitandukanye, uburyo butandukanye bwo gusubiza mu buzima bw'abaturage mu gihugu, n'ubushobozi bwo gusobanura abarwayi batandukanye mu bihugu bitandukanye no mu buryo butandukanye bwo guhitamo abarwayi bagomba gupimwa kugira ngo bagaragaze ko bafite COVID-19, harimo no gupima guhura.
Mu ntangiriro z'ukwezi kwa Werurwe 2020, abaganga bo mu turere twatewe n'iki cyorezo mu Butaliyani bavuze ko 10% by'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho byihutirwa mu gihe ibitaro n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi byo muri ako karere byageze ku rwego rwo hejuru.
Amakuru y'abanduye COVID-19 mu bitaro na/cyangwa mu kigo cy'ubutabazi bwihutirwa ko ubu ari 6% na 1% by'abanduye gusa mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ibihugu by'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'ubumwe (EU/EEU/EEU) ntabwo agaragaza amakuru).
Ariko kandi, igomba gukusanywa mu buryo bwemewe kugira ngo hagire amakuru y'ubugenzuzi agereranywa n'umubare w'abamaze kubura n'umubare w'abapfuye.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu 2010-11 bwagaragaje ko mu Burayi hari itandukaniro rikomeye mu kubona ibitanda by'ubuvuzi bukomeye n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi bw'ibanze, aho mu Budage habaye ibitanda 29.2 ku bantu 100,000 mu baturage b'u Burutuguki.
Ibi bivuze ko ibihugu bishobora kugira amafaranga menshi cyangwa make ugereranyije n'u Butaliyani (12,5 mu bitaro by'ubutabazi bw'imyanya y'imbere n'imbere mu bitaro by'ibanze ku muntu umwe mu 2010-2011).
Mu byiciro by'iterambere bijyanye no guhuza umubare w'ibitaro by'uburwayi, hagendewe ku bipimo by'ibihugu by'ubumwe bw'u Burayi/EEA n'u Bwongereza by'uko byatangaza ko umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bafungirwa mu bitaro ari wo ugomba kwibaniraho n'ibipimo > 90% by'ibyago byo kurenza urugero rw'umubare w'ibitanda by'uburwayi bw'imyanya y'imbere, byerekanwe mu isesengura rya gatandatu rya ECDC ry'ibyago byihutirwa bya COVID-19.
Kubera ko umubare w'abarwayi wiyongera mu turere tumwe na tumwe two mu bihugu bya EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza, ndetse no mu bitaro n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi byihutirwa bisanzwe bikora ibikorwa byo guhangana n'abaturage b'akarere, amakuru ku byerekeye abarwayi n'ibitanda by'ubuvuzi byihutirwa agomba kuba ahaboneka mu gace k'ibaruramari ry'ibaruramari ry'ibanze (NUTS-2).
Imibereho y'u Butaliyani n'iy'ibindi bihugu bigaragaza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 ku isi cyose gitera imbere mu buryo bwihuse muri EU/EEA no mu Bwongereza.
Ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo byita ku byihutirwa bigomba kwitegura uburyo bwo guhangana n'icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 no kongera umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bakeneye kwitabwaho, cyane cyane mu bihe by'ihutirwa, nk'uko biri mu ntara zagize ingaruka mu Butaliyani.
Nkuko byavuzwe mu isuzuma ry'akaga riherutse gukorwa, kurwanya SARS-COV-2 mu buryo bwihuse kandi bufatika ni ngombwa kugira ngo umuntu ashobore gutinda gukwirakwira, ahindukiriye uburyo bwo kugabanya, kuko kwiyongera mu buryo bwihuse kwitezwe mu mubare w'abanduye bishobora kudatanga umwanya uhagije wo gufata imyanzuro ku bayobozi n'ibitaro, bakumva, bakemera kandi bagakora ibyo bakora mu gihe bitakozwe mbere y'igihe.
Gusuzuma ibyago byihutirwa kandi byongera ku rutonde rw'ingamba z'ubuzima rusange zo kugabanya ingaruka z'icyorezo ku isi.
Hari amahirwe make ibihugu bifite ubushobozi bwo kongera imbaraga mu kurwanya SARS-COV-2 no kugabanya ibibazo by'ubuzima.
Iyo ibyo bitagenze neza, birashoboka ko gahunda z'ubuvuzi mu bindi bihugu bya EU/EEA zizagerwaho n'umubare munini w'abarwayi bakeneye kwitabwaho byihutirwa mu minsi cyangwa mu byumweru bizaba bikurikira.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), cyatewe n'indwara y'ubuhumekero (SARS) coronavirus 2 (SARS-CoV-2), kugeza ubu kimaze guhitana abantu barenga 3,000, cyateje abandi barenga 80,000 mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bice by'isi, cyateje impanuka kamere.
Mu buryo nk'ubwo, virusi yayo, SARS-CoV, yateje SARS abantu ibihumbi mu 2003, SARS-CoV-2 ishobora no kwambuka umujyi ikayigaragaza mu buryo bumwe.
Ariko kandi, COVID-19 ifite ubukana n'ubwandu buke ugereranyije na SARS ariko ni bwo bwanduye cyane kandi bugira ingaruka ku bantu bakuru ugereranyije n'abakiri bato, n'abagabo ugereranyije n'abagore.
Kubera ko umubare w'ibitabo byandika iby'indwara ziterwa n'indwara wiyongera vuba, iyi ngingo igerageza gutanga ibitekerezo byuzuye kandi ku gihe ku ngingo y'ubushakashatsi igenda yiyongera.
Tubagezaho ibishingiye ku makuru y'ibanze y'indwara z'ibyorezo, inkomoko y'indwara, kwiga virusi, gupima, kuvura, kumenya impamvu zitera ububabare no kwirinda ububabare.
Nubwo hari ibibazo byinshi bikeneye ibisubizo, twizeye ko iyi myumvire ishobora gufasha gusobanukirwa ingaruka z'imibabaro iterwa n'uburwayi.
Umunsi mukuru w'ihangu wo ku itariki ya 25 Mutarama 2020 wabaye urwibutso rutazibagirana ku Bashinwa bose bamenyeshejwe ko bari mu biruhuko mu byumweru byinshi nyuma y'icyorezo cya virusi nshya.
Iyi virusi ihuriye cyane na coronavirus (CoV) yateje indwara ikomeye y'ubuhumekero (SARS) mu mwaka wa 2003; ku bw'ibyo, yashyizweho izina rya SARS-CoV-2 n'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) ku wa 11 Gashyantare 2020, naho indwara ifitanye isano na yo yitwa COVID-19 (COVID-19).
Iki cyorezo cy'indwara y'ibicurane cyatangiye mu mujyi wa Wuhan mu Bushinwa, cyakwirakwira mu gihugu hose ndetse no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi hose.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 2 Werurwe 2020, virusi imaze gutuma abantu barenga 80,000 banduye COVID-19, abagera ku 40,000 bakize abandi barenga 3,000 barapfa.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima rivuga ko COVID-19 ari "umwanzi wa mbere w'abaturage" kandi ko ishobora kuba ikomeye kurusha iterabwoba.
Nkuko PubMed (https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/) ibivuga, mu gihe kitarenze amezi abiri, hasohotse ibitabo birenga 200 ku COVID-19 birimo icyorezo cya virusi, icyorezo cy'indwara, icyigisho cy'inkomoko yacyo, ubushakashatsi n'ubuvuzi kugeza ku wa 7 Mutarama 2020 aho byatangajwe bwa mbere bigaragaza uburyo virusi yanduye abarwayi batandukanye.
Iyi nyandiko igamije gusobanura neza uko ubushakashatsi buteye imbere mu bijyanye n'ingingo nshya.
Igihe cyose bishoboka, tugerageza kugereranya COVID-19 na SARS n'indi ndwara yatewe na COVID-19, indwara yo mu mutwe yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati (MERS, 2012).
Reka tuganire ku byo twize kugeza ubu, dusobanukiwe impamvu zituma umuntu agira ububabare, n'ibindi bibazo by'ingenzi.
COVID ni indwara idatera urupfu ku bantu, ikaba ari yo ituma abantu bagera kuri 15% bahura n'indwara ya Coronavirusi 4.
Icyakora muri iki gihe, twahuye n'indwara zikomeye ziterwa na CoVs mu bantu inshuro ebyiri, nka SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, zatumye habaho icyorezo cyatangiye mu Bushinwa mu 2003 no muri Saudia mu 2012, bikurikirana, cyakwirakwira mu bindi bihugu byinshi, kigahitana abantu benshi kandi kigahitana abantu benshi.
Bityo rero, COVID-19 ubu ni icyorezo cya gatatu cya COVIDV cyanditswe mu mateka y'abantu.
Nkuko byagaragajwe na Gisenyi 1,1, amoko y'abafite ubukana butamenyekanye yavuzwe bwa mbere mu mujyi wa Wuhan ku wa 31 Ukuboza 2019 ku rwego rw'igihugu rw'ubuzima mu Bushinwa.
Nyuma y'iminsi irindwi, icyorezo cya CoV cyasohotse.
Ku itariki ya 15 Mutarama 2020, mu mujyi wa Wuhan habayeho urupfu rwa mbere.
Muri icyo gihe, indwara y'icyorezo y'indwara ya cyera yakwirakwiriye mu mijyi, mu ntara no mu birwa by'abaturanyi.
Ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama, abaganga batangajwe ko bashobora kurwara indwara, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko abantu bashobora kwanduza.
Ku itariki ya 23 Mutarama, mu mujyi wa Wuhan hashinzwe itegeko ribuza abantu gutwara imodoka.
Ku itariki ya 24 Mutarama, ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bwakozwe ku ndwara y'indwara bwagaragaje ko mu barwayi 41 banduye, 21 gusa ari bo bagiranye isano n'isoko ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja rya Wuhan, rifatwa nk'aho ari ahantu hatangiriye icyorezo cy'ibinyabuzima bitamenyekanye.
Ku itariki ya 30 Mutarama, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangaje ko icyorezo ari ikibazo cy'uburwayi ku isi hose.
Mu gihe iyi raporo yari igaragaye, icyo cyorezo cyari cyarakwirakwiriye mu Bushinwa no mu bihugu hafi 50 byo hirya no hino ku isi.
Kubera ko ibintu bigenda bihinduka vuba, ubukana bw'icyo cyorezo n'ubwinshi bwacyo ni byo bizaba.
Ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare 2020, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu bigo byinshi ku barwayi 8,866 barimo abarwayi 4,021 bemejwe ko bafite COVID-19 bwagaragaje uburyo bwavuguruwe cyane ku ndwara y'indwara nk'ubu (https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UIBi-HX_rHPXa1qHA2bhdA).
SARS-CoV-2 ibasira abantu bose bafite imyaka yose ariko cyane cyane abafite imyaka 30-65.
Hafi kimwe cya kabiri (47.7%) cy'abafashwe n'iyo ndwara bari bafite imyaka irenga 50, bake cyane bari munsi y'imyaka 20, naho 14 gusa bari munsi y'imyaka 10.
SARS-CoV-2 yibasira abagabo benshi (0.31/100,000) ugereranyije n'abagore (0.27/100,000).
COVID-19 yakwirakwiriye mu matsinda menshi mu karere ka Hubei no mu karere kaho.
COVID-19 yatwaye iminsi 5 (2-9) kuva igihe cyo gupima.
Igihe cy'imibonano mpuzabitsina cy'iminsi 4,8 (3.0-7.2) ni cyo cy'ibanze.
Igihe cy'urupfu cye ku kigero cy'iminsi 9.5 (4,8-13).
Umubare w'ibanze w'ibyaremwe (RO) wari 3.77 (95% Cl: 3.51-4.05), naho uwo wasimbuwe wari 2.23-4.82.
Umubare w'abarwayi wiyongereye cyane mbere y'itariki ya 23 Mutarama 2020, mu gihe cy'ibihe by'imodoka nyinshi mu birori byo mu gihembwe mu Bushinwa.
Urupfu rw'abarwayi bafite ubwandu bwemejwe rwari 1.44% (95% CI: 1.10-1.86%), naho urwego rw'abapfuye rw'abarwayi rwahinduwe rwari 3.06% (95% CI: 202-4.59%).
Ibintu bitatu byateje COVID-19 akaga cyane ni imibonano mpuzabitsina (ubukwe), imyaka (>=60), n'imyanya ndangagitsina mibi.
CoVs ni umuryango muto w'ingirabuzima fatizo nini cyane zigizwe n'umushinga umwe w'ubwonko bwa RNA.
Bishobora kugabanywa mu byiciro bine, urugero nka alpha, beta, gamma na delta, ibyo alpha na beta bizwi ko bibaho ku bantu.
Igiterwa cy'umusemburo cy'umusemburo (S) cyumva mu ngirabuzimafatizo yacyo ingirabuzimafatizo ya angiotensin-transformer enzyme 2 (ACE2) na dipeptidyl peptidase 4 (DPP4) ya SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, hakurikijwe uko bikurikijwe, hanyuma igiterwa cy'umusemburo kigatera.
ADN ya virusi ihita isohoka mu cytoplasma; iyo virusi imaze kwera, ADN ya virusi ihita ihita ihita ihita ihura n'uruhu.
Icyiciro cya mbere cya genome ya SARS-CoV-2 cyatangajwe ku ya 10 Mutarama 2020.
SARS-CoV-2 yagaragaye ko ari ubwoko bushya bwa beta-CoV bufite ubushobozi bwo kumenya ADN y'abantu barenga 99.98% mu byiciro 10 bikurikirana byavanywe mu isoko rya mbere ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja rya Huanan mu mujyi wa Wuhan.
SARS-CoV-2 ifite inkomoko y'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima isa na SARS-CoV ugereranyije na MERS-CoV
Binyuze mu gutumiza électron mu buryo bw'ibinyabuzima, ibimenyetso bya SARS-CoV-2 byabonetse mu gice gito cyane cy'urwingo rw'ubuhumekero bw'abantu.
ACE2 mu bantu yabonetse ko ari yo ifite SARS-CoV-2 ndetse na SARS-CoV.
Ariko kandi, poroteyine ya S ya SARS-CoV-2 ikora ku bantu ACE2 mu buryo butoroshye kurusha SARS-CoV, ibyo bikaba byatewe n'uko SARS-CoV-2 ituma abantu barwara indwara z'uburwayi zisanzwe ari nto ugereranyije na SARS-CoV.
SARS-CoV-2 ishobora no gukora poroteyine ngufi idasanzwe hamwe na orf3b na poroteyine ikorwa na orf8.
Orf3b ya SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kugira uruhare mu kwandura virusi no guhagarika ibisobanuro bya IFNB; nyamara, nta hantu na hamwe hazwi ko orf8 ikora cyangwa ko ifite ubushobozi.
Ku wa 18 Gashyantare 2020, Zhou, et al., yatangaje uburyo bwa cryo-EM bufite umuvuduko uhagije wa ACE2 ku bantu aho 2.9 A ari ihame ry'umusemburo wa amino acid B0AT1.
Basanze uwo murambo, wahise ufungura kandi ukagenga ibimenyetso, twawushyize mu murambo nk'aho ari udakomeye kandi ADCE2-B0AT1 ishobora guhuriza hamwe poroteyine ebyiri za S, zigaragaza ko ari zo zemeza ko umuntu afite COVID na virusi itera ubumuga.
B0AT1 ishobora kuba intego y'ubuvuzi mu bushakashatsi bw'imiti yo kwirinda ubwandu bwa SARS-CoV-2.
Indwara z'ibanze n'iz'ibanze.
Byagaragaye ko SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV byakomotse ku mashusho y'ibinyabuzima byanduye, maze bikagera ku bantu binyuze mu makoteri n'ingamiya.
Binyuze mu kugereranya amateka y'ubwoko bwa SARS-CoV-2 n'ubundi bwoko bwa CoV, umugera wa nimugoroba wagaragaye nk'indwara y'ubwandu bw'ibanze bwa SARS-CoV-2 kuko virusi nshya ihuriyeho 96% n'izindi SARS-CoV ebyiri z'umugera wa nimugoroba ziswe umugera wa nimugoroba-SL-CoVZX45 na sensor-SL-CoVZX21.
Ariko kandi, icyatumye virusi ibasha kwambuka ikirere cy'ibinyabuzima, ndetse igakwira ku bantu, n'ubu ntikiramenyekana, kandi inzira yo kuyinyura iracyari itaramenyekana.
Ji, et al., bashinja inzoka ko ari zo zisanzwe zitwara virusi mu mubiri, zikaza zikazishyira ku bantu, harimo n'imiterere y'ibinyabuzima byo mu bwoko bwa S.
