SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV zishobora kubaho mu byumba amasaha 48 mu gihe cy'ubushyuhe ndetse n'iminsi 5 munsi ya 20C na 40%-50% by'umwotsi.
SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kugira uburyo nk'ubwo.
Bivugwa ko SARS-CoV-2 ibona izuba n'ubushyuhe bwa 56C mu minota 30, ether, 75% ya ethanol, ubwandu buhitana harimo chlorine, paracétic acid, chloroform n'ibindi birungo by'ubumara, ariko atari chlorhexidine, bishobora gukuraho virusi mu buryo bwiza.
Muri rusange, abantu bose bafite ubushobozi bwo kwirinda SARS-CoV-2 bityo bakaba bashobora guhura na virusi nshya.
Kugeza ubu, nta bushakashatsi bwimbitse bwagaragajwe bushingiye ku buryo umubiri ukira SARS-CoV-2.
Ku bw'ibyo, dushobora kwerekeza gusa ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe mbere y'uko COVID ibaho, cyane cyane SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV (Igishushanyo (Igishushanyo) (Igishushanyo) 4).
Ubusanzwe, iyo virusi imaze gutera umuntu urwaye, uburwayi bushobora kumenyekana n'ubwirinzi bw'umubiri binyuze mu buryo bw'ubumenyi bw'ibimenyetso (PRR yo) harimo C-type lectin net sensors, Toll-like sensors (TLR), NOD-Like sensors (NLR) na RIG-l-like sensors (RLR).
Binyuze mu buryo butandukanye, virusi ishobora gutuma imyuka igaragaza ubwivumbure, imiterere y'ingirabuzimafatizo z'ibinyabuzima by'ibinyabuzima, no gukora interférone y'umwanya wa I (IFN yo) igatuma virusi idakira kandi igatuma macrophage phagocoytosis igenda yihuta cyane.
