Gukoresha ijambo "kwitarura abantu" byatumye abantu bagira amacakubiri mu rwego rw'imibereho aho gukangurirwa gushyikirana n'abandi mu buryo nk'ubwo. Bamwe mu bayobozi batanze inama z'ubuvuzi ku bijyanye n'imibonano mpuzabitsina mu gihe cy'icyorezo cy'isi yose.
Muri ibyo harimo inama yo gukora imibonano mpuzabitsina n'uwo mwashakanye gusa, udafite virusi cyangwa ibimenyetso byayo.
Gushyira mu kato mu ngo byasabwe ku bantu bagaragaye ko bafite COVID-19 kandi bakeka ko bafite.
