Inama z'ubugenzuzi zatanzwe ku bantu bafite ibyago byinshi.
Abashoboraga guhura n'umuntu ufite COVID-19 kandi baherutse kwimukira mu gihugu cyangwa akarere gikwirakwijwe n'indwara, bagiriwe inama yo kuguma mu kato k'iminsi 14 guhera igihe aheruka guhura na we.
Uburyo bwo kurwanya ubwandu ni uguhagarika cyangwa kugabanya, no kugabanya.
Kuhagarika ibikorwa by'ubwandu bikorwa mu bihe bya mbere kandi bifuza gushakisha no gushyira mu kato abanduye no gushyiraho izindi ngamba zo kurwanya ubwandu no gukingira kugira ngo indwara itagenda ikwirakwira mu baturage.
Iyo nta buryo bwo guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'indwara bushoboka, imihati iba igamije kugabanya ikwirakwira ry'iyo ndwara no kugabanya ingaruka igira ku buzima n'imibereho myiza y'abaturage.
Uburyo bwo guhagarika no kugabanya bishobora gukorwa icyarimwe.
Kugabanya ibipimo bisaba ingamba zikomeye zo guhangana n'icyorezo ku isi hose, mu kugabanya umubare w'ibanze w'abanduye ku munsi wa 1.
Ibi bigabanya ibyago byo gutakaza serivisi z'ubuzima kandi bigatuma habaho igihe kinini cyo gukora inkingo n'imiti.
Mu bikorwa by'ubuvuzi bigamije kurwanya ubwicanyi harimo kwirinda umuntu ku giti cye, nko mu isuku, kwambara udupfukamunwa no kwirinda; ingamba zo kwirinda kwirinda ubwirinzi nk'imfungwa z'amashuri no guhagarika abategetsi b'amateraniro; kwitabira ibikorwa by'abaturage mu rwego rwo kubasaba kwakira no kwirinda ibyo bikorwa; ndetse n'ingamba zo mu rwego rw'ibidukikije nko gusukura ikirere. Mu Bushinwa hashyizweho ingamba nyinshi zidakuka zo guhagarika ubwicanyi igihe habayeho ubwicanyi, nko guhagarika ingendo mu mijyi yose no gushyiraho ingamba zikomeye zo guhagarika ubwicanyi.
Ibihugu bindi na byo byashyizeho ingamba zitandukanye zo kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
