Uburyo bwiza bwo kugabanya ubwandu bushobora kugabanya umubare w'abapfa 2/3 by'abapfa, ariko n'ubu bufite ingaruka ku bapfa ibihumbi amagana n'uburyo bwo kwivuza bwamaze gucibwa.
Guhangayika bishobora guhitamo ariko bigomba gukomerezwa igihe cyose virusi ikwirakwira mu bantu (cyangwa kugeza igihe urukingo ruzabera, niba ibyo bitinze), bitabaye ibyo, guhangayika bizatinda kabiri iyo intambwe ziguye.
Kwihanganira ku buryo burambye guhangana n'icyorezo cy'indwara ku isi hose, bituma habaho ibibazo by'imibereho n'ubukungu.
Nta muti wihariye wa virusi itera COVID-19 wemejwe, ariko hari ingamba zo kuwukora, harimo no gupima imiti ikomeje.
Gufata imiti y'ibanze, kunywa umutobe no kuruhuka bishobora gufasha kugabanya ibimenyetso.
Bisaba ko umuntu ahumeka, akagira umwuka wa ogisijeni, akagira amazi yo mu maraso, kandi akagira ubufasha bwo guhumeka.
Gukoresha steroïdes bishobora gutuma ingaruka z'iyo miti zidakora neza.
Ibindi birungo byinshi byemewe mbere yo kuvura izindi ndwara za virusi birimo gushakishwa niba bishobora gukoreshwa mu kuvura COVID-19.
OMS ivuga kandi ko "imiti imwe n'imwe yo mu rugo" ishobora kugabanya ibimenyetso byatewe na SARS-CoV-2.
OMS yatangaje ko kongera ubushobozi no guhuza uburyo bwo kwita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 ari ingamba y'ingenzi yo guhangana n'iki cyorezo.
ECDC n'ibiro by'umuryango w'abibumbye by'ubuzima (OMS) by'i Burayi byashyize ahagaragara amabwiriza ku bitaro n' serivisi z'ubuzima bw'ibanze yo kwimura ibikoresho mu byiciro byinshi, harimo gushyira imbaraga mu bikorwa bya laboratwari mu gupima COVID-19, guhagarika uburyo bwo gutoranya igihe cyose bishoboka, gutandukanya no gushyira mu kato abarwayi ba COVID-19, ubushobozi bwo kwita ku byihutirwa binyuze mu gutoza abakozi no kongera umubare w'abatanga umwuka n'ibitanda bihari.
Hari amakuru menshi avuga aho icyorezo cya mbere cy'indwara ya Ebola (cyitwa "indwara ya Ebola") cyavuye.
Umuntu wa mbere wamenyekanye ko afite coronavirus nshya ashobora kuba ari mu Ukuboza 2019 mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Mu gihe cy'ukwezi, umubare w'abanduye coronavirus muri Hubai wiyongereye buhoro buhoro.
Ibi byibanda ku isoko ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja rya Huanan, na ryo ryatangaga ibinyabuzima, igitekerezo kimwe ni uko virusi yavuye muri imwe muri izo nyamaswa; cyangwa, mu yandi magambo, ifite inkomoko y'indwara z'amatungo zikwirakwira ku bantu. Itsinda ry'ibinyabuzima byitwa buruki ryataburuwe ku wa 26 Ukuboza, rivurirwa na Muganga Zhang Jixian mu bitaro bya Hubei Provincial Hospital, wabimenyesheje Wuhan Jianghan CDC ku wa 27 Ukuboza.
Ku itariki ya 30 Ukuboza, itsinda ry'abaganga bo mu bitaro bya Wuhan Central Hospital ryagabishije bagenzi babo ko "koronavirusi ya SARS".
Abaganga umunani muri abo, barimo Li Wenliang, batanze inama ku gipolisi ku gukwirakwiza amakuru y'ibinyoma, mu gihe mu bindi, Ai Fen, yacyashyizweho n'abayobozi be kubera ko yatumye haba ubwoba.
Ubuyobozi bw'ubuvuzi bw'akarere ka Wuhan bwatanze itangazo ku mugaragaro ku wa 31 Werurwe, ryamenyesheje Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima.
Aba baganga b'i Wuhan batangajwe ko hari umubare munini w'abanduye indwara z'indwara z'igituntu zitazwi, batangiye gukora iperereza mu ntangiriro za Mutarama. Mu bihe bya mbere by'iki cyorezo, umubare w'abanduye wikubye inshuro zirenga 7 ku munsi.
Mu ntangiriro no mu gicamunsi cya Mutarama 2020, iyi virusi yageze mu bindi bice by'u Bushinwa, mu gihe mu gihe cy'umwaka mushya w'u Bushinwa, Wuhan ari cyo kigo cy'ingendo n'ikibuga kinini cy'amagare.
Ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama, Ubushinwa bwavuze ko ku munsi umwe habayeho abantu bashya bagera ku 140, barimo abantu babiri i Beijing n'umuntu umwe wabonetse i Shenzhen.
Amakuru yemewe agaragaza ko abantu 6.174 bari bamaze kugaragaza ibimenyetso byo kurwara mu mpera z'itariki ya 20 Mutarama 2020, ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe, Amerika yarushijeho gutwara Ubushinwa n'u Butaliyani ku mubare munini w'abantu banduye ku isi.Ku itariki ya 9 Mata 202o, ku isi hose hari abantu basaga miliyoni 1.61 banduye; abantu basaga 97.000 bapfuye naho abandi 364 bakize.
