Mu mpera za Mutarama, leta y'Ubushinwa yatangije gahunda yo guhindura ibintu, nyuma yaho ikaba yarasobanuye umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka ry'abakomunisiti mu Bushinwa Xi Jinping ko "irwanya abantu" mu rwego rwo guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'iyi virusi.
Ibi byiswe "ikigeragezo gikomeye kurusha ibindi byose byabayeho mu mateka y'abantu", byatangajwe ku wa 23 Mutarama, bihagarika ingendo z'abimukira binjira n'abasohoka i Wuhan, bigatuma ibisagara 15 by'umurwa mukuru wa Hubei byongera, bigira ingaruka ku baturage bagera kuri miliyoni 57.
Mu murwa mukuru w'u Rwanda, imodoka z'abikorera zabuzanyijwe.
