Abayobozi batangaje ko hashyizweho ibitaro by'agateganyo, ibitaro bya Houshenshan, byasojwe mu minsi 10.
Nyuma yaho, hari undi bitaro byubatswe, ibitaro bya Leishenshan, kugira ngo byakira abarwayi bashya.
U Bushinwa bugiye guhindura ibindi bitaro 14 byo mu mujyi wa Wuhan, birimo ibigo by'amakoraniro n'ibibuga by'indege. Ku itariki ya 26 Mutarama, leta yashyizeho ingamba zo guhagarika icyorezo cya COVID-19, harimo gutanga ibimenyetso by'ubuvuzi ku bagenzi no kongera ikiruhuko cya Pasika.
Amashuri n'amashuri byafunzwe mu gihugu hose.
Intara za Hong Kong na Macau zashyizeho ingamba nyinshi, cyane cyane ku mashuri n'amashuri makuru.
