COVID-19 yageze muri Koreya y'Epfo iturutse mu Bushinwa.
Ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe ubuzima cyatangaje ko ku itariki ya 20 Gashyantare habayeho kwiyongera kw'abanduye, ahanini bikaba byatewe n'abantu bari bateraniye i Daegu mu idini rishya rya Shincheonji Church of Jesus.
Abasenga Shincheonji bazaga i Daegu baturutse i Wuhan bakekwaho kuba ari bo batangije iki cyorezo.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 22 Gashyantare, abakirisitu 9,336, abagera ku 1,261 cyangwa 13% bavuze ibimenyetso. Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje ko ku itariki ya 23 Gashyantare 2020 ari yo yabaye iya mbere mu kwihangana.
Ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare, muri Koreya hemejwe ko hari abantu barenga 2,000 banduye, ariko ku itariki ya 29 Gashyantare hazamutse hagera ku bantu 3.150.
