Itariki y'indege nayo yarahungabanyijwe, bityo irahindurwa. Koreya y'Epfo yashyizeho gahunda ya mbere kandi ikomeye ku isi yo gupima abantu banduye iyi virusi, gushyira mu kato umuntu wese ufite ubwandu, no gukurikirana no gushyira mu kato abanduye.
Mu buryo bwo gupima harimo gutanga amakuru y'ibimenyetso by'abantu bavuye ku isi yose bakoresheje porogaramu ya telefoni, kujya ku gupima virusi ku munsi ukurikiyeho, no kongera ubushobozi bwo gupima abantu 20.000 ku munsi.
Porogaramu ya Koreya y'Epfo yabonetse ko ihamye mu kurwanya guhungabana nubwo nta karantine iri mu mijyi mikuru yose.
Abaturage benshi bo muri Koreya bashyize umukono ku nyandiko ivuga ko gukura Moon ku butegetsi ari uguhenda leta mu bikorwa by'iterabwoba cyangwa se ko yashyize hejuru uko yabyitwayemo.
Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, byavuzwe ko Koreya y'Epfo ifite icyorezo cya mbere cy'abarwayi ku munsi mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bine.
Ku itariki ya 29 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko guhera ku itariki ya 1 Mata, abagenzi bose bavuye mu mahanga bazajya mu kato k'ibyumweru bibiri.
Nkuko byatangajwe n'itangazamakuru ku itariki ya 1 Mata, Koreya y'Epfo yabonye ibisabwa byo guhagarika ibizamini by'iyi virusi mu bihugu 121 bitandukanye.
Irani yatangaje ko icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 cyabonetse bwa mbere ku wa 19 Gashyantare i Qom, mu gihe nk'uko Minisiteri y'Ubuzima n'Uburezi bw'Abafite Ubumuga bubitangaza, abantu babiri bapfuye nyuma y'uwo munsi.
Leta yatangaje ingamba zihutirwa zirimo guhagarika ibitaramo n'ibindi bikorwa by'umuco, imyidagaduro, amasengesho yo ku wa Gatanu, no gufunga kaminuza, amashuri yisumbuye n'amashuri.
Irani yashyize hanze miliyari eshanu z'amadolari y'amanyamerika yo kurwanya iyi virusi.
Perezida Hassan Rouhani yavuze ko ku wa 26 Gashyantare 2020 nta gahunda yo kwimura abantu mu duce tw'iwabo yagezweho n'iki cyorezo, abantu gusa nibo bazajya mu kato.
Mu kwezi kwa gatatu nibwo hatangajwe gahunda yo guhagarika ingendo mu mijyi, nubwo imodoka nyinshi zari zigiye gutangira guhagarara hagati y'imijyi mbere y'Umwaka mushya wa Nowrus.
Ibibanza by'Amashyaka by'Abashiya biracyari bifunguye kugeza ku wa 16 Werurwe 2020, Irani ikaba yabaye icyicaro cy'icyorezo cya virusi inyuma y'Ubushinwa muri Gashyantare.
Ibivugwa mu bihugu birenga icumi ku bijyanye no guhisha imipaka y'ubwicanyi muri Iran, byakurikiranye na Irani ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare, bikaba bigaragaza ko imipaka y'ubwicanyi iri hasi ugereranyije n'ibyabaye 388 byatangajwe na leta ya Irani kuri uwo munsi.
Inteko Ishinga Amategeko ya Irani yafunzwe, mu bagize Inteko Ishinga Amategeko 23 muri 290 bavuga ko bari mu kato ku itariki ya 3 Werurwe.
Ku itariki ya 12 Werurwe, Ikigo gishinzwe uburenganzira bwa muntu cyashishikarije abayobozi ba gereza zo muri Irani kurekura ku mugaragaro abarwanashyaka b'uburenganzira bwa muntu bafunzwe bazira ibitekerezo bitandukanye, ndetse no kurekura by'agateganyo abagororwa bose.
Yavuze ko hari ibyago bikomeye byo gukwirakwiza virusi mu bigo byafunze nka gereza, aho badafite ubuvuzi buhagije.
Ku itariki ya 5 Werurwe, Leta ya Irani yatangaje ko abantu 100 bapfuye ku munsi umwe, ari umubare munini w'abantu bapfuye mu gihugu kuva ubwo ubwicanyi bwatangira.
Abayobozi 12 b'inama cyangwa abahoze ari abanyapolitiki ba Irani n'abayobozi ba leta bapfuye bazize iyo ndwara mu mpera z'ukwezi kwa gatatu.
Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, Irani yari ifite abantu 50 bagerwaho n'icyorezo cya Corona buri saha n'umuntu umwe upfa buri minota icumi.
Nkuko byatangajwe n'abayobozi b'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima, hari amakuru avuga ko mu gihugu cya Iran hashobora kuba hari abantu barenga batanu mu barwaye.
Hari kandi igitekerezo cy'uko ibihano Amerika yafatiye Irani bishobora kugira ingaruka ku bushobozi bw'ubukungu bw'igihugu bwo guhangana n'icyorezo cya virusi.
Intumwa nkuru y'umuryango w'abibumbye ishinzwe uburenganzira bwa muntu yasabye ko ibihugu byugarijwe cyane n'icyorezo cy'isi, harimo na Iran, bikuramo ingamba zo kugabanya imigabane y'ubukungu.
Iki cyorezo cyemejwe ko cyakwirakwiriye mu Butaliyani ku wa 31 Mutarama, ubwo abashyitsi babiri b'Abashinwa basangaga SARS-CoV-2 i Roma.
Ibibazo by'abapfuye byatangiye kwiyongera cyane, bituma leta ya Irani ihagarika ingendo zose z'indege ziva mu Bushinwa zijya mu Bushinwa, ndetse itangaza ko ibintu byihutirwa.
Itsinda ry'abanduye COVID-19 ryaje kumenyekana, ritangira ku bantu 16 bemejwe muri Lombardy ku wa 21 Gashyantare. Ku wa 22 Gashyantare, Umutwe w'Abaminisitiri watangaje ko hashyizweho itegeko rishya ryo guhagarika ubwicanyi, harimo gushyira mu kato abantu barenga 50,000 bo mu turere 11 two mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani.
Minisitiri w'Intebe Giuseppe Conte yagize ati "Ahantu icyorezo cyageze, kwinjira no kuva mu gihugu ntibizashyirwa ahagaragara.
Muri ibi bice byategetswe guhagarika imirimo y'akazi n'ibiganiro bya siporo. " Mu kwezi kwa gatatu, leta y'u Butaliyani yategetse gufunga burundu amashuri yose n'imiryango mu gihugu hose, ubwo Ubutaliyani bwageze ku 100.
Imikino yose y'imikino, harimo n'imikino y'umupira w'amaguru muri Serie A, yagombaga kubera ahantu hafungiye, ariko ku itariki ya 9 Werurwe, imikino yose yahagaritswe burundu nibura ukwezi kumwe.
Ku wa 11 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Conte yategetse ko ibikorwa hafi ya byose by'ubucuruzi bihagarikwa uretse ibigo binini n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi. Ku wa 6 Werurwe, Ikigo cy'ubucuruzi, guhagarika ingufu, kongera ubuzima bw'umuntu mu buryo bw'umubiri n'ubuvuzi bwihutirwa (SIAARTI) cyasohoye ibitekerezo by'ubuvuzi bivuga ko hari gahunda zitandukanye zishobora gushyirwa mu bikorwa.
Ku itariki ya 19 Werurwe, u Butaliyani bwarenze Ubushinwa buvamo igihugu gifite umubare munini w'abapfa bavuye kuri coronavirus ku isi ubwo bwarimo amakuru y'abantu 3,405 bapfuye kubera icyorezo cy'isi yose.
Ku itariki ya 22 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko u Burusiya bwashyize indege icyenda z'igisirikare mu Butaliyani nk'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 5 Mata, mu Butaliyani hemejwe ko habayeho abantu 128.98 bapfuye, abantu 15.887 bapfuye, n'abantu 21.815 bakize, abenshi muri bo bakaba bari mu ntara ya Lombardy.
Raporo CNN yashyize hanze igaragaza ko umubare munini w'abakuze mu baturage b'u Butaliyani hamwe n'ubushobozi buke bwo gupima abantu barwaye virusi bishobora gutuma habaho urupfu rwinshi.
Igisubizo cya virusi mu Bwongereza cyabanje kugaragara ko ari cyo cyoroshye cyane mu bihugu byibasiwe, kugeza ku wa 18 Werurwe 2020, leta y'Ubwongereza ntiyatangije gahunda yo gutandukanya abaturage cyangwa ingamba zo gushyira mu kato abantu benshi.
Ibi byatumye leta yanengwa kubera ko itafashe ingamba n'uburyo bwinshi bwo guhangana n'impungenge z'abaturage. Ku wa 16 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Boris Johnson yatangaje ko yibukije abaturage kujya mu materaniro atari ngombwa no guhuza n'abaturage, asaba abantu gukora mu ngo zabo igihe cyose bishoboka kandi bakirinda ahantu nk'ahantu hakorerwa imikino, hoteli na za sinema.
Ku wa 20 Werurwe, leta yatangaje ko ibigo byose by'imyidagaduro birimo utubari n'ibigo by'imikino bizajya bifunga vuba bishoboka, kandi isezeranya gutanga 80% by'imishahara y'abakozi ku kigero cya £2,500 buri kwezi mu rwego rwo gukumira ubushomeri mu gihe cy'ikibazo. Ku wa 23 Werurwe, Raisul Wasaraha yatangaje ingamba zikomeye zo kwitandukanya n'abaturage, kubuza abantu benshi guhurira hamwe no kwiba ingendo n'amazu yo guturamo, ibyo bikaba byarateganyijwe ko ari ngombwa.
Mu buryo butandukanye n'uko byari bimeze mbere, ubu buhagarikwa bwashyizweho n'igipolisi binyuze mu guhagarika ibikorwa no guhagarika amateraniro.
Ibigo byinshi byategetswe gufunga, uretse ibigo by'ubucuruzi byitwa ko ari "ibisumbuye", birimo ibigo by'ubucuruzi, amafarmasi, banki, ibigo by'ubwubatsi, ibigo by'ibikoresho by'ubwubatsi, ibigo by'ibikoresho by'ubwubatsi n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi.
Ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama, umuntu wa mbere wamenyekanye wanduye COVID-19 yemejwe mu majyaruguru y'uburengerazuba bwa Pasifika mu ntara ya Washington, avuye i Wuhan ku itariki ya 15 Mutarama.
Itsinda ry'abagize Inzu Nyezeri rifite uruhare mu kurwanya Coronavirus ryashinzwe tariki ya 29 Mutarama.
Ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama, ubutegetsi bwa Trump bwatangaje ko hari ikibazo cy'uburwayi bwa vuba, buhagarika abagenzi bavuye mu Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 28 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya indwara - ikigo cya mbere cy'ubuzima rusange muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika - cyatangaje ko cyakoze ibikoresho by'ubushakashatsi.
Ariko iyo tubikora, iperereza rya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika ritangira ku rugero ruto, ryihishe inyuma y'ubwoko nyakuri bw'ibiza.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ibikoresho by'ubushakashatsi by'ubudehe byatanzwe na leta y'u Burayi mu kwezi kwa Gashyantare, kubura kwemererwa n'ubudehe bw'ubushakashatsi bw'abikorera (mu mashuri yisumbuye, mu bigo by'imari n'ibitaro) kugeza mu mpera z'uku kwezi kwa Gashyantare, n'uburyo buciriritse abantu bakwiriye guhabwa ubushakashatsi kugeza mu ntangiriro za Werurwe (nyuma y'aho hakenewe inama z'ubuvuzi).
Ku itariki ya 27 Gashyantare, ikinyamakuru The Washington Post cyatangaje ko hari ubushakashatsi bushya bwagiriwe muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, butageze ku 4.000.
Mu mpera z'ukwezi kwa gatatu, Atlantic yatangaje ko nta bushakashatsi bwakozwe munsi ya 14.00.
Ku itariki ya 22 Werurwe, Associated Press yatangaje ko "abantu benshi bari bafite ibimenyetso n'amabwiriza y'abaganga bategereje amasaha n'iminsi kugira ngo basuzumwe". Nyuma y'urupfu rwa mbere rwavuzwe muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika muri leta ya Washington ku wa 29 Gashyantare, Guverineri Jay Inslee yatangaje ko ibintu byihutirwa, ibyo bikaba byakurikiwe n'ibindi bihugu.
Amashuri yo mu karere ka Seattle yahagaritse amasomo ku wa 3 Werurwe, mu gice cya kabiri cy'ukwezi kwa Werurwe amashuri yo mu gihugu hose yarafunzwe. Ku wa 6 Werurwe 2020, itsinda ry'abahanga mu ndwara z'ibyorezo muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, mu kigo cy'amashuri cy'i Londres, ryatanze inama ku byerekeranye n'ingaruka za virusi nshya ya corona mu gihugu.
Kuri uyu munsi Perezida Trump yashyize umukono ku itegeko ryo kwitegura no gusubiza mu buryo bukwiriye, ryatanze amafaranga y'amadolari miliyari 8.3 yihuta yo gushora imari mu bigo bya leta kugira ngo bisubire ku bwicanyi.
Ibigo by'ubucuruzi byashyizeho amategeko agenga ingendo, guhagarika amateraniro, no gushishikariza abakozi gukora imirimo yo mu rugo.
Imikino n'ibihe by'imikino byarahagaritswe. Ku wa 11 Werurwe, Trump yatangaje ko mu Burayi bwose, uretse mu Bwongereza, hari ibihano by'iminsi 30, bizatangira ku wa 13 Werurwe.3
Ku munsi wakurikiyeho, yaguye ibihano yongeraho mu Bwongereza no muri Irilande.
Ku itariki ya 3 Werurwe, yatangaje imimerere y'ubutagondwa mu gihugu hose, bituma amafaranga ya Leta y'u Burayi abaho mu rwego rwo guhangana n'ibiza.
Guhera ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe, ibigo byinshi by'ubushakashatsi byafunze cyangwa bigabanyiriza amasaha y'akazi muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika mu kugerageza kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Ku wa 17 Werurwe, icyorezo cyemejwe mu ntara 50 no mu Karere ka Columbia. Ku wa 23 Werurwe, mu mujyi wa New York habonetse abantu 10.700 banduye coronavirus, ni ukuvuga umubare munini ugereranyije n'uw'abanduye muri Koreya y'Epfo.
Ku wa 25 Werurwe, umuganga yavuze ko gutandukanya abantu n'abandi bishobora kuba bifite akamaro, kuko umubare w'abanduye wagabanutse ugera ku minsi 2,0 ugera ku minsi 4.7.
Kugeza ku itariki ya 28 Werurwe, hari abantu 32.308 banduye muri New York, n'abantu 672 bapfuye bazize virusi. Ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe, muri Amerika havuzwe ko habonetse abantu benshi banduye coronavirus kurusha mu bindi bihugu byo ku isi, harimo Ubushinwa n'u Butaliyani. Ku itariki ya 8 Mata, muri Amerika habonetse abantu 400,335 banduye, naho abapfuye bagera ku 12.841.
Nkuko itangazamakuru ryabitangaje ku wa 30 Werurwe, Perezida wa Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika Trump yafashe icyemezo cyo kongera itegeko ryo kwirinda abantu kugeza ku wa 30 Mata.
Kuri uwo munsi, ubwato bw'ibitaro USNS Comfort, bufite ibitanda hafi 1000, bwarohamye i New York.
Ku itariki ya 3 Mata, Amerika yongeyeho abantu 884 bapfuye bazize Coronavirus mu masaha 24 ashize.
Mu ntara ya New York, abantu barenga 100,000 bamaze kwandura iyi virusi ku itariki ya 3 Mata. Ibiro by'abungeri by'Amerika byamaganiwe ko bigabanya ibyago n'ubugenzuzi bw'amabwiriza, bigategeka abayobozi b'ubuzima n'abahanga mu bya siyansi gushyira hamwe ibitabo n'ingingo bijyanye na virusi mu biro by'umukuru w'igihugu Mike Pence.
Kuba Trump yarashyigikiye ibiza by'ibiza mu buryo bwuzuye, byatangiye kwibasirwa n'abavuga rumwe n'ubutegetsi.
Bamwe mu bayobozi ba Amerika n'abavuga rumwe na leta banenze ko Amerika yemera ko ibicuruzwa bikomeye, harimo n'ibikoresho by'ibanze by'ubuvuzi, bivanwa mu Bushinwa, ari iby'ingenzi cyane.
Ibaruramari ry'ingendo mu kirere ryakoreshejwe mu gushushanya no guhanura icyorezo cyasohotse mu kinyamakuru The Journal of Travel Medicine hagati muri Mutarama 202o.
Nkuko bigaragara mu makuru yo mu 2018 y'umuryango mpuzamahanga w'indege, Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo na Taipei ni byo byinjije abantu benshi cyane baturutse i Wuhan.
Dubai, Sydney na Melbourne na byo bivugwa ko ari ahantu hahurira abantu benshi cyane bavuye i Wuhan.
Bali ni imwe mu mijyi 20 ikunda gutembera cyane kurusha indi, naho umurwa mukuru wa Australia ukaba ari wo ukunda gutembera cyane. Australia yashyize ahagaragara gahunda yo guhita igaragaza ko ikomeje guhangana na Coronavirus (COVID-19) ku itariki ya 7 Gashyantare.
Bivugwa ko nta byinshi bizwi kuri COVID-19, ko Australia izashyira imbaraga mu gucunga imipaka no gutumanaho mu guhangana n'icyorezo ku isi.
Ku itariki ya 21 Werurwe, muri Ositaraliya hatangajwe ingamba zo kurinda abantu ibintu by'akaga gakomeye.
Kubera ko hari uburyo bwiza bwo gutwara abantu mu modoka z'indege mu mujyi wa Wuhan no muri Hubei, ibihugu byinshi byateganya gutura abaturage n'abambari mu karere, cyane cyane binyuze mu ndege z'igihugu zatanzwe mu kiruhuko cy'iza bukuru, abayobozi b'u Bushinwa batanga impushya z'ubwenegihugu.
Canada, Amerika, Ubuyapani, Ubuhinde, Sri Lanka, Ositaraliya, Ubufaransa, Arjantine, Jatmalka na Thailand ni bimwe mu bihugu bya mbere byasetse ku byerekeye imyuzure yo mu ngo z'abaturage.
Pakistan yavuze ko itazatura abaturage bayo mu Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 7 Gashyantare, u Burezili bwateye imyuzure mu gihugu cy'u Burezili, aho abantu 34 cyangwa abagize umuryango wabo, uretse bane bo muri Polonye, umwe wo mu Bushinwa n'umwe wo mu Buhinde, bari mu byabo.
Abaturage bo muri Polonye, Ubushinwa n'u Buhinde basubijwe mu gihugu cya Polonye, ubwo indege yo muri Brezili yahagaze hagati mbere yo kujya muri Brezili.
Umunya-Brazil wagiye i Wuhan yashyizwe mu kato mu kigo cya gisirikare kiri hafi ya Brasília.
Kuri uwo munsi, abantu 215 bari mu birombe bya Canada (176 bari mu ndege ya mbere, 39 bari mu ndege ya kabiri yari yahawe serivisi na Leta ya Amerika) bavuye i Wuhan bajyanwa muri CFB Trenton mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare, indege y'indege y'indege y'u Canada 185 yavuye i Wuhan, yageze mu kibuga cy'indege cya CFB Trenton.
Abayobozi ba Australia bahaye umugisha abaturage 277 ku wa 3 na 4 Gashyantare mu kigo cy'ibohero cya Christmas Islands, cyashyizweho ahantu ho kwiherera, aho bamaraga iminsi 14.
Indege y'indege y'indege ya New Zealand yageze i Auckland ku wa 5 Gashyantare, kandi abagenzi bayo (harimo abavuye muri Australia no mu nyanja ya Pasifika) bari mu kato ku kigo cy'ingabo z'inyanja cya Whanaparoa, mu majyaruguru ya Auckland.
Ku wa 15 Gashyantare, Amerika yatangaje ko igiye kohereza abasirikare b'Abanyamerika ku bwato bwa Diamond Princess.
Ku wa 21 Gashyantare, indege yari itwaye abagenzi 129 bo muri Canada yavuye muri Diamond Princess yageze i Trenton, Ontario.
Mu ntangiriro z'ukwezi kwa Werurwe, Leta y'u Buhinde yatangiye kohereza abaturage bayo muri Irani. Ku itariki ya 14 Werurwe, indege ya South African Airways, yo mu gihugu cya Afurika y'Epfo, yasubije abaturage 112 bo muri Afurika y'Epfo.
Hakozwe igenzura ry'ubuvuzi mbere yo kujya muri Afurika y'Epfo, 4 bagaragaje ibimenyetso bya coronavirus basiga hanze kugira ngo bagabanye ibyago.
Abanyarwanda bavuye muri Afurika y'Epfo gusa ni bo basubijwe mu gihugu cyabo.
Ibyavuye mu iperereza byerekana ko abantu bose bo muri Afurika y'Epfo, harimo abakozi b'indege, abagenzi, abakozi bo muri hoteli, Polisi n'abasirikare bari mu bikorwa by'ubutabazi, bose bari mu kato mu gihe cy'iminsi 14 muri Ranch Resort.
Ku itariki ya 20 Werurwe, Amerika yatangiye kuvana ingabo zayo muri Iraki kubera ko yari ifite ikibazo cy'intambara.
Ku wa 5 Gashyantare, Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'u Bushinwa yatangaje ko ibihugu 21 (harimo Belarus, Pakistan, Trinidad na Tobago, Misiri na Iran) byohereje ubufasha mu Bushinwa.
Abanyeshuri b'Abashinwa bo muri za kaminuza zo muri Amerika bateraniye hamwe kugira ngo bafashe kohereza ibikoresho by'ubwonko byanduye mu Bushinwa, aho itsinda ry'abafatanyabikorwa bo mu gace gakomeye ka Chicago ryavuze ko ryabashije kohereza udupfukamunwa 50,000 twa N95 ku bitaro byo mu karere ka Hubei ku wa 30 Mutarama.
Ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batangaje ko bahawe miliyoni 100 z'amadolari y'ubuntu na OMS mu rwego rwo gushyigikira ubushakashatsi ku nkingo no mu bikorwa byo kuvura, mu gihe "abantu bari mu kaga muri Afurika no muri Aziya" barindwa.
Interaksyon yatangaje ko leta y'Ubushinwa yatanze udupfukamunwa 200,000 muri Filipine ku wa 6 Gashyantare, nyuma y'aho umunyapolitiki Richard Gordon ashyigikiye udupfukamunwa miliyoni 3.16 i Wuhan.
Ku itariki ya 9 Gashyantare, Umuryango Mpuzamahanga w'Abasangwabutaka w'i Singapuru watangaje ko ugiye kohereza inkunga ya miliyoni 2.26 z'amadolari mu Bushinwa.
U Buyapani bwatanze udupfukamunwa miliyoni imwe mu byo mu maso mu mujyi wa Wuhan, u Turukiya bwatanze ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, u Burusiya bwatanze ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi birenga toni 13 mu mujyi wa Wuhan, Malaysia itangaza ko yatanze udupfukamunwa miliyoni 18 mu Bushinwa, u Budage bwatanze ibikoresho bitandukanye by'ubuvuzi ku barwayi 10.000 bo mu bwoko bwa Hazmat, naho Amerika itanga toni 17.8 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Bushinwa kandi isezeranya ko izajya iha inkunga y'amafaranga y'amiriyoni 100 mu bihugu byugarijwe n'icyo cyorezo. Nyuma y'aho Ubushinwa bwagaragaraga ko bwashyize mu gaciro, igihugu cyatumye inkunga yo gufasha ibihugu bitandukanye byugarijwe n'icyorezo cy'isi.
