Ububiligi bwasubije amasiki 100.000 atagomba gukoreshwa, bivugwa ko yaturutse mu Bushinwa ariko mu by'ukuri akaba yaturutse muri Kolombiya.
Ku rundi ruhande, inkunga y'Ubushinwa yakiriwe neza mu bice bimwe na bimwe bya Amerika y'Epfo na Afurika. Ku itariki ya 2 Mata, Banki y'Isi yatangiye inkunga yihutirwa y'ibikorwa mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere.
OMS yashimye cyane ibyo abayobozi b'u Bushinwa bakoze mu kurwanya no gukumira ibiza.
OMS yavuze ko ari yo yarwanyaga icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2002-2004, aho abayobozi b'u Bushinwa bashinjwa guhisha ibikorwa byo kwirinda no kugenzura, n'icyorezo kiriho ubu mu gihe leta nkuru "igatanga amakuru mashya yo kwirinda impungenge mu biruhuko byo mu mwaka mushya wa Lunar".
Ku wa 23 Mutarama, mu gusubiza ku cyemezo cy'ubuyobozi bw'igihugu cyashyizeho itegeko ribuza abantu gutembera mu mujyi wa Wuhan, uhagarariye OMS Gauden Galea yavuze ko atari "inama ya OMS", ahubwo ko ari "igitekerezo cy'ingenzi cyo guhagarika icyorezo aho cyagwiriye cyane" maze agitanga "ubutagondwa mu mateka y'ubuzima bw'abaturage". Ku wa 30 Mutarama, ubwo umukuru w'umuryango w'abibumbye yemezaga ko ari we urimo kwanduza abantu mu Bushinwa no mu bindi bihugu, OMS yatangaje ko gukingira abantu ari ikibazo cy'uburwayi byihutirwa mu buzima bw'abaturage (PHEIC), ndetse ko ari icyorezo cya gatandatu cyakozwe mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya 2009 cy'icyorezo cya Coronavirus.
Umuyobozi mukuru w'umuryango w'abibumbye wita ku buzima, Tedros Adhanom, yavuze ko PHEIC "igomba gukwirakwira ku isi hose, cyane cyane mu bihugu bifite amikoro make n'ayibanze bidafite gahunda ikomeye y'ubuzima.
Mu gusubiza ku bikorwa byo guhagarika ingendo, Tedros yavuze ko "nta mpamvu yo gufata ingamba zitagombye guhuza neza n'ingendo n'ubucuruzi mpuzamahanga" kandi ko "OMS idashyigikira ko ingendo n'ubucuruzi bigabanuka".
Ku wa 5 Gashyantare, OMS yasabye umuryango mpuzamahanga gutanga miliyoni 675 z'amadolari yo gushyigikira gahunda yo kwitegura ibihugu bifite amikoro make, igaragaza ko byihutirwa gushyigikira ibyo bihugu "nta gahunda ziriho zo kumenya abantu banduye virusi, nubwo yaba yaravutse".
Tedros yakomeje avuga ko "dukomeye gusa kubera ko imishyikirano yacu idakomeye" asaba umuryango mpuzamahanga "guhora ushyiraho imari cyangwa ugatanga indi myinshi ejo". Ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare, OMS yatangaje ko COVID-1 ari yo ndwara.
Kuri uwo munsi, Tedros yavuze ko Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye, Antonio Guterres yemeye guha "ububasha uburyo rusange bw'Umuryango w'Abibumbye bwo kugira icyo bukoraho".
Itsinda ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buterankunga ryashyizwe mu bikorwa kubera ibi byavuyeho, riha uburenganzira ubufatanye muri rusange mu bikorwa by'Umuryango w'Abibumbye, WHO ivuga ko "buzatuma twibanda ku bikorwa by'ubuzima mu gihe ibindi bigo bishobora gutanga ubumenyi mu guhangana n'ingaruka zikomeye z'imibereho myiza, ubukungu n'iterambere ry'icyorezo".
Ku wa 14 Gashyantare, itsinda ry'ibikorwa rihuriye ku rwego rw'igihugu riyobowe na OMS rifite Ubushinwa ryashyizwe mu bikorwa kugira ngo intiti mpuzamahanga na OMS mu Bushinwa bafashe mu gucunga aho hantu no gupima "uburemere n'icyorezo" binyuze mu gukora amaseminari n'inama ku bibazo by'ingenzi by'igihugu no gukora ingendo ku mbuga nkoranyambaga kugira ngo "basuzume ingaruka z'ibikorwa byo kwitabira ku rwego rw'intara n'ubwigenge, harimo mu bice by'umujyi no mu cyaro". Ku wa 25 Gashyantare, OMS yatangaje ko "igomba gukora byinshi mu rwego rwo kurwanya icyorezo cy'icyorezo cy'icyorezo cy'icyorezo cya Coronavirus ku rwego mpuzamahanga, nubwo hari igihe cyo "kwitegura icyorezo cy'icyorezo" ku isi hose.
Mu rwego rwo guhangana n'ubwicanyi bukomeje muri Irani, OMS yohereje itsinda ry'umurimo rihuriye mu bikorwa kugira ngo rigenzure iki kibazo. Ku wa 28 Gashyantare, abayobozi ba OMS bavuze ko ibipimo by'ubwandu bwa Coronavirus ku rwego mpuzamahanga bizamurwa kuva ku "kirenga" kugera ku "kirenga", ku rwego rwo hejuru, ku miburo n'igishushanyo mbonera cy'akaga.
Mike Ryan, umuyobozi mukuru w'ishami ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima bwa vuba, yatanze umuburo mu ngingo yagize ati "Iki ni ikimenyetso cy'ukuri ku butegetsi bwose ku isi:
Iyi virusi ishobora kuba iri mu nzira kandi ugomba kuba witeguye", avuga ko ingamba z'uko umuntu yabyitwaramo neza zishobora gufasha isi kwirinda "ikintu kibi cyane".
Ryan yavuze ko amakuru y'iki gihe atagira gihamya y'uko abayobozi b'ubuzima bw'abaturage batangaza ko ari icyorezo cy'isi yose, avuga ko gutangaza ko ari icyorezo "bisobanura ko mu by'ukuri twemera ko umuntu wese ku isi ariwe urwara virusi.
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe, OMS yatangaje ko Coronavirus ari icyorezo cy'isi yose.
Umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS yavuze ko "arahangayikishijwe cyane n'ibipimo biteye ubwoba by'icyorezo n'ibyago, ndetse n'ibipimo biteye ubwoba by'ubushomeri". OMS yahanganye n'ibitotezo bikomeye ku kintu gisa n'aho kitari gihagije mu kurwanya icyorezo ku isi, harimo gutangaza mu gihe cyashize icyihutirwa cy'ubuzima bw'abaturage no kubona virusi nk'icyorezo ku isi hose.
Muri ibyo birego harimo n'isaha yo gusaba umuyobozi mukuru w'umuryango w'abibumbye w'abibumbye Tedros Adhanom ko agomba kwegura, yashyizweho umukono n'abantu 733.000 ku itariki ya 6 Mata.
Ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe 2020, inzobere mu by'uburenganzira bwa muntu z'Umuryango w'Abibumbye zongeyeho ko uburenganzira bwa buri wese buhabwa agaciro mu gihe cy'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Itsinda ry'impuguke ryavuze ko buri wese afite uburenganzira bwo gukora ibikorwa byo kurokora ubuzima kandi ko leta ari yo izabiha inshingano.
Amatsinda y'abantu yashimangiye ko kuba nta mafaranga cyangwa ubwisungane mu kwivuza bitagombye gutuma umuntu agirirwa urwikekwe.
Abahanga bemeje ko buri wese afite uburenganzira ku buzima, harimo abafite ubumuga, ab'inzego z'ibanze, abakuze, abimukira, abatagira aho baba, abafite ibibazo by'ubukene, abari muri gereza, ndetse n'impunzi n'abandi bantu batamenyekanye bakeneye inkunga ya leta.
Ibigo bya leta mpuzamahanga byatangaje ingaruka z'ubukungu n'imibereho myiza y'abaturage z'icyorezo cya COVID-19.
Ishyirahamwe ry'ubufatanye mu bukungu n'iterambere ryatangije urubuga rwo gutanga amakuru yuzuye mu gihe gikwiriye ku buryo ibihugu byo ku isi byitabira, ndetse n'ibitekerezo n'inama.
Kuva ku buryo bwo gushimangira gahunda z'ubuzima n'ubukungu ku isi kugeza ku kuganira ku ngaruka z'icyorezo n'ibihano by'abimukira, ikigo cy'ikoranabuhanga, harimo n'Ikigo cy'Itegeko Nshinga, kigamije gufasha ibihugu kwiga no korohereza ibikorwa mpuzamahanga byo guhuza mu kurwanya icyorezo cya Coronavirus.
Leta y'Ubushinwa yanenze Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika, Minisitiri w'Intebe w'u Bwongereza Michael Gove, n'umuhungu wa Perezida wa Brazil Jair Bolsonaro, kubera uko yitwaye ku cyorezo cy'icyorezo cyugarije intara ya Hubei mu Bushinwa.
Imibare y'abayobozi b'intara mu ishyaka ry'abakomunisiti mu Bushinwa (CPC) yarushijeho kwiyongera ku buryo bwihanganiraga imihati yo gushyira mu kato mu Bushinwa bwo hagati, igaragaza ko batanyuzwe n'uko politiki zagiye zitabira gutandukana n'abo baturage.
Abasesenguzi bavuga ko iyo ngingo yagamije kurinda umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka rya gikomunisiti ry'u Bushinwa Xi Jinping guhunga mu buzima kubera icyorezo cya Coronavirus.
Bamwe mu bayobozi b'u Bushinwa, urugero nka Zhao Lijian, bahakanye ko icyorezo cya Coronavirus cyaturutse i Wuhan, batekereza ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyaturutse muri Amerika cyangwa mu Butaliyani.
Ubuyobozi bwa Donald Trump muri Amerika bwise coronavirus "virusi y'Ubushinwa" cyangwa "virusi ya Wuhan" buvuga ko ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu Bushinwa bwatumye iyi virusi ihinduka icyorezo cy'isi yose", abashinja ko ari urwango kandi ko yatumye abantu batamenya uko ubutegetsi bwayo bunanirwa kurwanya iki cyorezo".
Ikinyamakuru Daily Beast cyasanze amakuru ya leta ya Amerika agaragaza ko hari amakuru y'ibinyoma yatanzwe n'Inama y'Umutekano w'Igihugu, avuga ko "byose bivuga ku Bushinwa.
Twabwiwe ko tugomba kugerageza kwakira ubwo butumwa mu buryo bwose bushoboka, harimo inama z'abanyamakuru n'amashusho kuri televiziyo". Ibinyamakuru nka Politico, Politiki y'Ibindi bihugu na Bloomberg byavuze ko ingamba z'Ubushinwa zo kohereza imfashanyo mu bihugu byugarijwe na virusi ari kimwe mu byo bigamije kwangiza isi.
Umuyobozi ushinzwe politiki y'amahanga y'umuryango w'ubumwe bw'ubumwe bw'uburayi, Josep Borrell, yaburiye ko hari "amakimbirane mu rwego rw'isi, harimo n'intambara yo kwigarurira igihugu binyuze mu bikorwa by'ubushyamirane n'ubwiyandarike.
Borrell yagize ati "Ubushinwa burimo bwemeza ko Amerika ari inshuti nziza kandi yiringirwa".
Ubushinwa kandi bwasabye Amerika gukuraho abana muri Syria, Venezuela na Iran, bwoherereza inkunga ibihugu byombi.
Imyitozo ya Jack Ma yo gutanga udupfukamunwa 100,000 muri Cuba yahagaritswe n'ibihano by'Amerika ku itariki ya 3 Mata.
Abategetsi ba Amerika bashinjwa kandi ko batanga imfashanyo ku bindi bihugu.
Hari ibibazo byatangajwe ku bijyanye n'imyambaro hagati y'ibindi bihugu, urugero nk'u Budage, Otirishiya, Uswisi; na Repubulika ya Tchèque n'u Butaliyani.
Uretse ibyo, Turukiya yafashe imashini z'ubuhumekero zigera mu magana, zijyanwa muri Esipanye.
Mu ntangiriro z'ukwezi kwa Werurwe, Leta y'u Butaliyani yamaganye ishyirahamwe ry'ubumwe bw'u Burayi ku kutagira uburemere ku Butaliyani bwandujwe na coronavirus.
Maurice Massari, ambasaderi w'u Butaliyani muri EU, yavuze ko "Ubushinwa bwonyine ari bwo bwashubije mu buryo bw'uburyo bubiri.
Nta gushidikanya, ibyo si ikimenyetso cyiza cy'ubwiyunge bw'Abanyaburayi".
Ku itariki ya 22 Werurwe, nyuma yo guhamagara ku murongo wa telefoni Minisitiri w'Intebe w'u Butaliyani Giuseppe Conte, Perezida w'u Burusiya Vladimir Putin yateguye ko ingabo z'u Burusiya zohereza mu Butaliyani abaganga ba gisirikare, imodoka zihariye zifasha mu kurwanya indwara z'ibyorezo n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubuvuzi.
Ikinyamakuru Stampa cyo mu Butaliyani cyatangaje ko "isoko ry' politiki ridafite ishingiro" ryemeza ko 80% by'imfashanyo y'Uburusiya "itari nziza cyangwa nta cyo imaze ku Butaliyani".
Uyu mugabo yashinje u Burusiya ko butegura "ibikorwa by'ubutaka n'ubutegetsi bwa dipolomasi" mu gushyigikira ibikorwa byo gushakisha.
Perezida wa Lombardy, Attilio Fontana, na Minisitiri w'Ububanyi n'Amahanga wa Italy, Luigi Di Maio, bahakanye ibyo bitangazamakuru bagaragaza ko babishimiye.
Uburusiya kandi bwatumye indege yo gutwara abantu muri Amerika.
Umuvugizi wa Kremlin Dmitry Peskov yagize ati "iyo [Putin] ahawe inkunga n'inshuti z'Amerika, abona ko igihe abahanga mu by'ubuvuzi n'ibindi bikoresho by'Amerika bazaba bafite ububasha, bashobora no guhemba iyo bibaye ngombwa".
Imirwano ya gisirikare ya NATO "Defense 2020" yari iteganyijwe mu Budage, Polonye no mu bihugu bya Baltique, ni yo mirwano ikomeye kurusha izindi ya NATO kuva Intambara y'Icyitso irangiye, izaba ku rugero ruto.
Umunyamabanga mukuru w'Ikigo cy'Ingabo zishinzwe gutunganya intwaro za kirimbuzi Kate Hudsan yanenze itangazo ry'ingabo za 2020 agira ati "icyorezo cy'ubuzima bw'abaturage kiriho ubu, kitateza akaga ubuzima bw'abasirikare ba Amerika n'ibihugu byinshi by'Uburayi gusa, ahubwo n'abatuye ibihugu bikorera". Leta ya Iran yahuye n'ingaruka zikomeye za virusi, imaze guhitana abanyamuryango bagera kuri mirongo ibiri b'Inteko Ishinga Amategeko hamwe n'abandi bategetsi ba politiki 15 b'ubu cyangwa ba kera.
Perezida wa Iran Hassan Rouhani yandikiye abayobozi b'isi ibaruwa rusange ku wa 14 Werurwe 2020, asaba ubufasha avuga ko igihugu cye kirambiwe guhangana n'ikibazo cy'uburwayi kubera ko nta ruhushya rw'ibicuruzwa mpuzamahanga ruhabwa n'Amerika kubera ko Amerika yagabanyije abana ku gihugu cya Iran.Iki cyorezo cyatumye Amerika isaba gushyira mu bikorwa uburyo bw'uburinganire bw'imibereho myiza kurusha ibindi bihugu, harimo kwita ku buzima bw'isi yose, kwita ku bana ku isi hose, ikiruhuko cy'umuryango cy'umushahara, n'amafaranga menshi y'ubwisungane mu kwivuza.
Abahanga mu by'imibereho ya politiki bavuga ko bizagira ingaruka mbi ku byiringiro bya Donald Trump byo kongera gutorwa mu matora y'umukuru w'igihugu yo mu mwaka wa 2020.
Koreya y'Epfo yanenze "imyidagaduro y'ubwirinzi ikomeje gukorwa" nyuma y'aho u Buyapani bwatangaje ko umuntu wese uvuye muri Koreya y'Epfo azajya mu kato k'ibyumweru bibiri mu duce leta yateganyije.
Umuryango wa Koreya y'Epfo wari umaze igihe utabona uko Perezida Moon Jae-in yabyitwayemo.
Abanyakoreya benshi basinye ku nyandiko yo gutangaza ko Moon azakuwe ku butegetsi kubera ibyo bavuze ku bijyanye no kurwanya ubutegetsi bubi, cyangwa gushimira ku buryo bwabwo. Icyorezo mpuzamahanga cyatumye ibihugu byemera gushyiraho itegeko rihutirwa ryo kubwitegereza.
Bamwe mu basesenguzi bagaragaje impungenge ko bizatuma ubutegetsi bwongera ubushobozi.
Muri Hongiriya, inteko ishinga amategeko yatoye ko Viktor Orban, umunyapolitiki w'umunyacyorezo, ashyiraho amategeko atagira aho ahuriye n'amacakubiri, ahagarika inteko ishinga amategeko ndetse n'amatora, kandi agahanira abantu bakekwaho gukwirakwiza amakuru y'ibinyoma ku virus n'uburyo leta ikora ku byago.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus cyashinjwe ko hari igihe cy'ibura ry'ibikoresho, bitewe n'uko hakoreshwa ibikoresho byo kurwanya ubwicanyi, kugura kubera ubwoba, n'ibibazo by'inganda n'ibikorwa byo gutanga ibikoresho.
Ikigo gishinzwe ibiribwa n'imiti muri Amerika cyatanze umuburo ku bijyanye no kugabanuka kw'imiti n'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi kubera ko abakoresha ibiyobyabwenge bakomeza kwifuza ibiyobyabwenge n'ababiha ibiyobyabwenge.
Mu duce tumwe na tumwe kandi habayeho kugura ibintu by'ubwoba byatumye ibigo by'ubucuruzi bifungwa, urugero nk'ibiribwa, impapuro zo mu bwiherero n'amazi ya plastike, bituma ibicuruzwa bigabanuka.
Uruganda rw'ikoranabuhanga rwaburiye cyane ko rwari rwaratinze gutwara ibikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga.
Nkuko byatangajwe n'umuyobozi mukuru w'Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima, Tedros Adhanom, ko umubare w'ibikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwa muntu wikubye inshuro 100.
Ibi byatumye ibiciro by'ubuvuzi byiyongeraho inshuro makumyabiri ugereranyije n'ibisanzwe, bikaba byaratumye no gutanga imiti byongera gutinda mu byumweru bine kugeza kuri bitandatu.
Ibi byatumye ku isi hose hakomeza kubura ibikoresho byo kwirinda, aho Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryavuze ko ibyo bishobora guteza akaga abakozi b'ubuzima.
Muri Ositaraliya, icyorezo cy'indwara ya parasiyo cyatumye haboneka uburyo bushya mu gihe ibigo by'ubucuruzi by'abakozi bigurisha ibicuruzwa byo muri Ositaraliya mu Bushinwa.
Ibi byatumye amata y'abana acika intege mu maduka manini, nyuma yaho Leta ya Ositaraliya ikabuzanya. Kubera ko COVID-19 ikwirakwira mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani no mu ntara ya Wuhan, ndetse n'uko hakenewe ibiribwa byinshi, ibi bice byombi byarokotse ibihano bikomeye by'amafaranga.
Ingamba z'Ubushinwa n'u Butaliyani zo kurwanya ikoreshwa ry'ibikoresho by'ubushyuzi n'ubucuruzi butemewe n'amategeko by'ibicuruzwa by'ubumara zagiye zigira icyo zigeraho, zirinze kubura ibyokurya bikomeye byari byitezwe mu Burayi ndetse no muri Amerika ya Ruguru.
Mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani, aho usanga hari umusaruro munini w'ubuhinzi, nta cyo bivuze ku kwiyahura, ariko ibiciro bishobora kwiyongera ugereranyije n'abashinzwe ubuhinzi.
Imyanya y'ubucuruzi y'ibiribwa itagira aho igera yahuye n'ibigo by'ubucuruzi by'ibiribwa by'agateganyo, ndetse no mu mujyi wa Wuhan, aho leta y'Ubushinwa yafashe ingamba zo gutanga imfashanyo ku bikoresho by'imirire y'ingurube mu rwego rw'ubugenzuzi bw'ibanze.
Mu Butaliyani, hari itegeko nk'iryo rigenga ibyo kurya bigomba kubikwa mu gihe cy'imimerere y'ubwihutirwa.
Umusaruro w'ubukungu ku isi yose wagaragaye mu Bushinwa: nk'uko raporo y'itangazamakuru yo ku wa 16 Werurwe ibigaragaza, ubukungu bw'u Bushinwa bwagize ingaruka zikomeye mu mezi abiri ya mbere ya 2020 kubera ingamba za leta zo guhagarika ikwirakwira rya virusi, ibicuruzwa by'ubucuruzi byagabanutseho 20.5%.
Kubera ko Ubushinwa ari isoko rikomeye ry'ubukungu n'ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi, icyorezo cya virusi cyagaragaye ko cyateje ubwoba bwinshi bw'ihungabana rikomeye mu bukungu bw'isi.
Agathe Demaris wo mu kigo cy'abagenzuzi b'imari, yavuze ko ibiciro bizagenda bihinduka kugeza igihe hazaba hari ibipimo bifatika by'ibisubizo.
Mu kwezi kwa mbere 2020, bamwe mu bashakashatsi bagaragaje ko ubukungu bw'isi buzamuka bitewe n'icyorezo cya SARS, ku isi hose buzamera nk'aho bwarenze urugero rw'icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2002-2004.
Igereranya ryatanzwe n'impuguke muri Washington University mu mujyi wa St. Louis ryatanze miliyari 300 z'amadolari y'Amerika ku rwego rw'isi yose mu kugura ibintu bishobora kumara imyaka ibiri.
Ishyirahamwe ry'ibihugu by'abatuza peteroli mu mahanga (OPEC) ryashenguwe n'ibibazo by'ubukene bw'ibiciro by'ibitoro kubera ikibazo cy'ubukene bw'u Bushinwa.
Ibiciro by'ibicuruzwa by'iyi soko byagabanutse ku wa 24 Gashyantare kubera umubare munini w'abanduye COVID-19 hanze y'u Bushinwa.
