Ibipimo bitatu byose by'ibiciro by'ibicuruzwa byaranze iki cyumweru bigabanutseho 10%.
Kugeza ku wa 28 Gashyantare, ikigo cy'ubugenzuzi cya SCope Ratings GmbH cyemeje ko igenzura ryigenga ry'ibyago by'ishoramari ry'Ubushinwa, ariko ryakomeje kuba mu buryo butari bwiza.
Mu kongera kugwa kw'ibicuruzwa bishingiye ku bwoba bwa virusi ya corona, ku wa 16 Werurwe nibwo habaye ugucika cyane.
Abantu benshi babona ko hari igihe ubukungu buzacogora.
Umushoramari Mohamed El-Erian yashimiye ingamba zabanjirije banki nkuru n'iya leta.
