Imirimo myinshi irimo abantu benshi yahagaritswe na leta n'ubutegetsi bw'igihugu, harimo n'ibirori ngarukamwaka bya Sand New, aho ibigo byigenga bifunga amaduka n'ibintu by'ingenzi nka Hong Kong Disneyland na Shanghai Disneyland.
Imirimo myinshi y'umwaka mushya w'ukwezi n'ibintu by'ingenzi by'ingenzi byafunzwe kugira ngo abantu batitabire, harimo mu mujyi wa Forbbiden i Beijing no mu nsengero z'umuco.
