Igisukura intoki cyangwa igica ibihuru mu ntoki ni igisubizwa intoki, bityo amazi akaba atagombye gukoreshwa.
Mu mpera z'imyaka ya 1990 no mu ntangiriro z'ikinyejana cya 21, ibiyobyabwenge byo guhumeka amazi bitagira icyo bimarira (bikanamenyekana nk'ibiyobyabwenge byo guhumeka amazi, ibiyobyabwenge byo kwica ibinyabuzima, cyangwa ibiyobyabwenge byo guhumeka amazi) byatangiye kumenyekana.
