Ujye ukaraba intoki mu mazi ashyushye cyangwa amazi y'amazi.
Amazi arimo gutembera ni meza cyane kuko amazi ahagaze ashobora guhumanya, kandi ubushyuhe bw'amazi ntibugira icyo butanga.
Mu gihe ukoresheje isabune, ujye ukoresha imyenda yo mu ntoki, mu ntoki no mu ntoki.
Amasabune atuma uruhu rwirinda ubwandu, kandi ubushakashatsi bugaragaza ko abantu bakoresha isabune bakaraba intoki neza kurusha iyo bakoresha amazi gusa.
Ujye utera hasi nibura amasegonda 20.
Iyo umuntu ashyushye, bituma amera nk'indimu, bityo bikamufasha guhita akuraho ubwandu bw'umubiri, bityo akongeraho ubundi butuma amera nk'indimu, agatanga ubwandu bwinshi ku mubiri.
Amazi arimo gutemba.
Kujya mu mirimo yo guhagarara bishobora gutuma amaboko asubira inyuma.
Gukoresha imyanda yo kumesa cyangwa guhumeka.
