Ibishyimbo by'ibishyimbo n'ibishyimbo by'amabara bishobora kwihisha munsi y'ibishyimbo.
Ubusanzwe, gukaraba intoki ni byiza kugira ngo intoki ntizigume zimye; uruhu rwumye rushobora gutera amakuba ku ruhu, bityo rukaba rwiyongeraho ibyago byo kwandura.
Hari ibintu bitandukanye byoroheje bishobora gukorwa kugira ngo ukore isuku y'amaboko byoroshye iyo amazi yo mu nzu y'amazi n'isabune ataboneka, nko kuvoma amazi mu nzu y'amazi cyangwa ahantu hari imyobo myiza no/cyangwa gukoresha imyanda mu gihe uri mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere.Mu gihe hari ikibazo cy'ubura bw'amazi (nk'amashuri cyangwa ahantu ho gutunganya amazi mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere), hari uburyo bwo kubika amazi, nko "kujya gutunganya amazi make" n'ibindi bintu bihenze.
