Gukaraba intoki neza ni ingenzi mu mikorere yo gusukura, ariko hari amakimbirane ku birebana n'akamaro ko gukaraba intoki mu bice rusange.
Ubushakashatsi bwinshi bwagaragaje ko imyanda y'amaboko ifite isuku kurusha iy'imyanda y'amaboko y'amaboko ifite amashanyarazi.
Mu mwaka wa 2008, ubushakashatsi bwakozwe na Kaminuza ya Westminster, mu mujyi wa Londres, bwashyigikiwe n'ikigo cy'inganda y'impuzu z'impapuro cyitwa European Tissue Symposium, mu kugereranya ibipimo by'isuku byatanzwe n'impuzu z'impapuro, ibiyobyabwenge byo guhumeka umwuka n'ibiyobyabwenge byo guhumeka umwuka.
Nyuma yo gukaraba intoki no kuzimya mu kirere gishyushye, umubare w'udukoko twavumbuwe mu maraso wazamutseho 194% n'ibipimo by'amaraso 254%.
Iyo umuntu ahumetse mu kirere, bituma bakteria z'intoki zongeraho 42% n'iz'ibinyabuzima byongerwaho 15%.
Nyuma yo gukaraba intoki no kuzihumeka, bakteria zigabanuka ku ntoki ku kigero cya 76% n'ibimenyetso ku kigero cya 77%. Abahanga mu bya siyansi bakoze kandi ibigo by'ubushakashatsi kugira ngo barebe niba hari ahantu ho gukaraba intoki no mu karere aho gukaraba intoki bishobora kuba byarakorwe.
Icyuma gisoza umwuka cyo mu ndege, kivamo umwuka ugenda ku muvuduko wa metero 180 ku gatsiko (650km/s; 400mph), cyabashije gusuka ubumara ku ntoki kandi cyanduza ahantu hamwe n'abaturage bakoreshaga aho bakoreraga n'aho bakoreraga ubwiherero, ku metero 2 z'uburebure.
Iyo ukoresheje umwuka ushyushye mu gikonshya, ubumara bushobora gukwirakwira mu birometero 0.25 mu gikonshya.
Mu 2005 mu bushakashatsi bwakozwe na TUV Produkt na Umwelt, hagaragajwe uburyo butandukanye bwo gutunganya intoki.
Hari impinduka zikurikira mu mubare w'udukoko nyuma yo gukaraba intoki:
Hariho ibigo byinshi bitandukanye bicuruza ibikoresho by'amaboko, kandi ibikoresho byo gukaraba byashyizweho mu kugereranya ibyo gukaraba impapuro.
Gukaraba intoki ukoresheje umurava w'amaboko ni ubundi buryo bwo gukora urugendo udafite isabune n'amazi.
Igisukura intoki gifite inzoga ku kigero cya 60%.
Imibereho myiza y'ubuzima yabaye itegeko nyuma y'aho Ignaz Semmelweis, umuganga wo muri Hongiriya, abonye akamaro kayo mu kurwanya indwara mu by'ibidukikije byo mu bitaro (1846).
Hari ibikoresho bya elegitoroniki bibutsa abakozi b'ibitaro ko bagomba gukaraba intoki mu gihe bibwiye ko bari kwibagirwa.
Ubushakashatsi bumwe bwagaragaje ko umubare w'abanduye wagabanutse bitewe n'uko bakoreshaga ibiyobyabwenge.
Gukaraba intoki mu gihe cy'amasegonda 15 ni uguhumba intoki mu gihe ukoresheje isabune nyinshi n'amazi cyangwa gel.
Amaboko agomba gukorakoranywa.
Niba hari imyanda iri munsi y'urugo, ushobora gukoresha burashi kugira ngo uyikureho.
Kubera ko ubwandu bw'ibicurane buba buri ku mazi y'amaboko, ni ngombwa ko aburanishwa neza, bityo akaza gukangwa akoresheje umwenda mwiza.
Nyuma yo gukonja, urumuri rw'amazi rushobora gukoreshwa mu gufunga amazi (kandi mu gihe bibaye ngombwa, mu gufungura amarembo y'irembo).
Jya wirinda gufata intoki zawe ukazikura muri ibyo bice.
Impamvu yo gukaraba intoki mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi ni ukwirinda ko inzige z'ibinyabuzima (zitwa "buzuku") zisanzuraho kandi zikirinda ko zikwirakwiza.
Ikinyamakuru New England Health cyanditse ko uburwayi bw'indwara y'indwara y'indwara y'indwara bwirengagizwa mu bigo by'ubuvuzi, aho abaganga benshi n'abakozi b'ubuvuzi bibagirwa gukaraba intoki mbere yo gukora ku barwayi, bityo bakajya batanga udukoko.
Ubushakashatsi bwagaragaje ko gukaraba intoki mu buryo bworoheje no mu bundi buryo bworoheje bigabanya ubwandu bw'amaraso mu mirwi y'ibishyimbo ku kigero cya 66. Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangaje ko impapuro zanditse ku kigero cy'imyenda n'imyenda y'ibishyimbo mu rwego rw'ubuvuzi.
Amabwiriza y'isuku y'amaboko y'ikigo ashobora kuboneka ku rubuga rwacu rwa interineti kugira ngo abaturage bayasuzume.
