Iyo myitozo yo kwica ishobora gukenerwa mbere yo kubagwa cyangwa mu gihe cyo kwicwa cyane. Ugomba gukubita intoki mu gikombe cy'uburwayi, niba ari ngombwa, ukagukuraho umwambi utariho icyo uvuze, ukaguhanaho chlorheydine cyangwa iodine, ukagushyiraho imyenda myiza yo gukaraba intoki nyuma yo gukaraba, ukagukuraho imyenda n'ibindi bikoresho by'isuku.
Ibishushanyo byose bigomba gucibwa.
Muri iyo gahunda, ukaraba intoki n'amaboko kugeza ku gikonjo, akenshi bisaba iminota 2 kugeza kuri 6.
Nta gihe kirekire cyo guhanagura (iminota 10) gikenewe.
Mu gihe ugiye mu mazi, amazi yo mu ntoki agomba guhagarara mbere y'uko asubira mu maboko.
Nyuma yo gukaraba intoki, intoki zigomba gukoreshwa imyenda isukuye kandi zikagomba gufungwa mu gihe cy'ubuvuzi.
Kugira ngo umuntu atagwirirwa arwara indwara, ni byiza koza intoki cyangwa gukoresha umuti wica intoki mbere na nyuma yo kwita ku muntu urwaye.
Mu kurwanya uburwayi bw'ibicurane mu bitaro, gukaraba intoki mu buryo bw'ingirakamaro cyane, byakozwe ku kigero cya 20% mu gihe umuntu yabaga yogeje intoki mbere y'uko aba, kandi bikagaragara ko ari bike cyane mu gihe umuntu yabaga yogeje intoki buri gihe, ku kigero cya 35%.
Gukaraba intoki ukoresheje isabune isanzwe, bigabanya inshuro eshatu indwara z'ubwandu bw'ibitekerezo mu biryo ugereranyije no gukaraba intoki ukoresheje isabune y'ubuhumekero. Ugereranyije no gukaraba intoki ukoresheje isabune y'ubuhumekero bw'ibitekerezo mu gihe gito, mu gihe cy'amasegonda 30 buri muntu, byagaragariye ko gukaraba intoki bikuraho utuntu tw'ibitekerezo 26% ugereranyije n'uko bakoresha isabune y'ubuhumekero.
Ariko isabune n'amazi biruta inzoga zo mu ntoki mu guhumeka intoki kubera icyorezo cya H1N1 cy'ibicurane A n'icyatuma intoki zigabanuka. Gukura intoki mu bikorwa by'ubuvuzi mu bigo by'ubuvuzi bishobora kuba bikubiyemo kwigisha abakozi gukaraba intoki, kongera ubushobozi bwo gukoresha inzoga zo mu ntoki, no kwibutsa abakozi ibyo banditse no kuvuga.
Hakenewe gukorwa ubundi bushakashatsi kugira ngo ibyo bintu biboneke neza mu buryo butandukanye bwo kwita ku buzima.
Mu bihugu bikiri mu nzira y'amajyambere, gukaraba intoki ukoresheje isabune ni byo by'ibanze mu buzima bw'abantu, ndetse no mu mirire myiza.
Ariko kubera ko amazi, isabune n'ibigo by'imyidagaduro bikenewe mu ngo, mu mashuri no mu kazi bidahagije, biragoye ko umuntu yibagirwa imyitwarire y'abantu ku isi.
Urugero, mu karere k'icyaro muri Afurika usanga hari imbuga z'ibyishimo nke cyangwa abantu benshi bafite imyanya y'ibyishimo mike, nubwo ari yo nzira ihenze yo kubaka ahantu ho kwidagadura.
Ariko, uburwayi ni imyifatire umuntu abura kubera kubura isabune n'amazi.
Gutangaza no guteza imbere ibyishimo ukoresheje isabune bishobora kugira ingaruka ku myanzuro y'amategeko, bishobora gutuma abantu bamenya akamaro ko kugira ibyishimo kandi bigatuma abaturage bagira ihinduka rikomeye ry'imyifatire.
Kugira ngo ibyo bigerweho neza, hakenewe kugenzura no gusuzuma.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe mu bushakashatsi 70 bwagaragaje ko uburyo bushingiye ku muryango bwongera ibyishimo mu mashuri y'abari mu muryango muto, mu gihe ubukangurambaga bwo gushimangira abaturage butagira icyo bugeraho. Urugero rumwe mu bikorwa byo kumenyekanisha ibyishimo mu mashuri ni "Icyitegererezo cy'inyenyeri eshatu" cya UNICEF, aho hashishikariza amashuri gufata ingamba zoroheje, zitaguzwe kugira ngo abana bishime n'isabune, ndetse n'ibindi bisabwa mu bijyanye n'isuku.
Iyo ugeze ku rwego rwo hasi, ishuri ritanga inyenyeri eshatu z'icyubahiro.
Gushyiraho ahantu ho kwidagadura bishobora kuba kimwe mu bigize gahunda yo kumenyekanisha ibyishimo mu rwego rwo kugabanya indwara n'urupfu rw'umwana.
Umunsi mpuzamahanga w'ibyishimo ni urugero rw'uburyo bwo guhagurutsa abantu kugira ngo bahindure imyitwarire. Kubera icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019-20, UNICEF irimo gukora ubukangurambaga bwo guhangana n'ibyishimo.
